OL,7,FMost of the subpostmasters expecting
OL,8,Fletters of exoneration after being
OL,9,Fcaught up in the Horizon scandal
OL,10,Fhaven't received them, as ITV News' UK
OL,11,FEditor Paul Brand reports
OL,13,FOnly 178 subpostmasters caught up in
OL,14,Fthe Horizon scandal have so far been
OL,15,Ftold that their convictions have been
OL,16,Fquashed.
OL,18,FThe Conservative government promised
OL,19,Fthat all those wrongfully convicted
OL,20,Fwould receive a letter exonerating
OL,21,Fthem by the end of July.
