OL,7,FHowever, the vast majority of the 700
OL,8,Fsubpostmasters who thought they would
OL,9,Fqualify for a letter have not yet
OL,10,Freceived one.
OL,12,FData provided by the Ministry of
OL,13,FJustice shows just a fifth have so far
OL,14,Fbeen sent the official correspondence,
OL,15,Fwhich states "The convictions on your
OL,16,Frecord have been quashed."
OL,18,FEarlier this year, the government
OL,19,Fpassed emergency and unprecedented
OL,20,Flegislation, officially exonerating
OL,21,Fall those wrongfully convicted.
