OL,12,FDavid - who doesn't wish to share his
OL,13,Fsurname - is in the minority who have
OL,14,Freceived a letter, though it was sent
OL,15,Fto his daughter.
OL,17,FHe moved to Portugal after being
OL,18,Fwrongfully convicted almost 20 years
OL,19,Fago, serving a two-month prison
OL,20,Fsentence.
