OL,7,F"I can hold my head up and say, my
OL,8,Fconviction's been quashed. Come on
OL,9,Fguys, look at me differently, and
OL,10,Fpeople are looking at me differently,"
OL,11,Fhe said, brought to tears.
OL,13,F"There were tears last night. That's
OL,14,Fhow it's affected us, in a good way,
OL,15,Fto know our conviction has been
OL,16,Fquashed, to say I'm not a criminal
OL,17,Fanymore."
