OL,7,F"There are an awful lot of inhibitors
OL,8,Fto people coming forward, and it's not
OL,9,Ftheir fault. It is the responsibility
OL,10,Fof the government and the Post Office,
OL,11,Fwho failed these people, to find them,
OL,12,Fvindicate them and compensate them."
