OL,7,FHe said: "I do understand what the
OL,8,Fdelay is. What I've heard is the
OL,9,FMinistry of Justice is saying there's
OL,10,Fmore cross-referencing of cases than
OL,11,Fwe thought in terms of identifying the
OL,12,Findividuals.
OL,14,F"I'm not in any shape or form trying
OL,15,Fto play party politics with this
OL,16,Fbecause I never have. But it's really
OL,17,Fimportant the new government and the
OL,18,Fnew ministers get hold of this, and
OL,19,Fdon't let it drift."
