OL,7,FIn a statement, the Ministry of
OL,8,FJustice spokesperson said: "The
OL,9,FHorizon scandal was an unprecedented
OL,10,Fmiscarriage of justice, and the
OL,11,FGovernment is working to notify all
OL,12,Fpostmasters whose convictions have
OL,13,Fbeen quashed as quickly as possible.
OL,15,F"We have sent 178 letters to wrongly
OL,16,Fconvicted sub postmasters and have
OL,17,Fcommitted to publishing monthly
OL,18,Fupdates on this figure commencing 3rd
OL,19,FOctober.
